'''Cynthia Cu''' is the doctor who introduced Richard for his presentation.

==History==
Cynthia introduced Richard before he started his presentation on his PATH pen. She talked about his decades of work in surgery and then turned the crowd over to him.

==Career==
She is a surgeon of some sort.
